nodes.text: The WED-15-D3 Treadwell was a model of maintenance droid produced by Cybot Galactica. After the original WED-15 Treadwell was discontinued due to low sales, the Cybot Galactica team received customer complaints about the move, and a request for new Treadwells. Responding to their customers, Cybot Galactica produced the WED-15-D3 several months later, marketed as a more affordable version of the original Treadwell.
